Custom Inference Logic Integration
In the previous chapters we didn‚Äôt talk about the src/sequence/inference.py file that exists in the src/sequence module, but if you pay attention in the training notebook, here‚Äôs what you would find:


notebooks/011-sequence-modeling.ipynb

